<ul>
<li>The Horizon 7.5.4 download page only has Agents. To see the rest of the files, use the <strong>Select Version</strong> drop-down to choose 7.5.3.<br/>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-39085 " src="https://i2.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/img_5e03512bd40cf.png?w=1100&#038;ssl=1" alt="" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/img_5e03512bd40cf.png?w=434&amp;ssl=1 434w, https://i2.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/img_5e03512bd40cf.png?resize=300%2C229&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 434px) 100vw, 434px" data-recalc-dims="1"/></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>If Horizon Toolbox is installed, uninstall it. You&#8217;ll have to <a href="#toolbox">reinstall</a> it later, including configuring the SSL certificate again (back up the certificate before uninstalling). Note: the Horizon Toolbox developers have not been updating Horizon Toolbox for newer versions of Horizon Connection Server.<br/>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21286 " src="https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/img_5a6483a0b4c69.png?w=1100" alt="" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/img_5a6483a0b4c69.png?w=594&amp;ssl=1 594w, https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/img_5a6483a0b4c69.png?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 594px) 100vw, 594px" data-recalc-dims="1"/></li>
<li>Run the downloaded <strong>VMware-Horizon-Connection-Server-x86_64-7.12.0.exe</strong>, <strong>VMware-Horizon-Connection-Server-x86_64-7.10.2.exe</strong> orÂ <strong>VMware-viewconnectionserver-x86_64-7.5.3.exe</strong> (ESB).<br/>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-39433 " src="https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/img_5e7223cda8d24.png?w=1100&#038;ssl=1" alt="" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/img_5e7223cda8d24.png?w=646&amp;ssl=1 646w, https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/img_5e7223cda8d24.png?resize=300%2C121&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px" data-recalc-dims="1"/><br/>
