<li>In the <em>Welcome to the Installation Wizard for VMware Horizon 7 Connection Server</em> page, click<strong> Next</strong>.<br/>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-10693 " src="https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/img_58ce709a13490.png?w=1100" alt="" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/img_58ce709a13490.png?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i1.wp.com/www.carlstalhood.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/img_58ce709a13490.png?resize=300%2C91&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" data-recalc-dims="1"/></li>
