<h3 id="replicaserver">Install Horizon 7 Replica Connection Server</h3>
<p>Additional internal Horizon Connection Servers are installed as Replicas. After installation, there is no difference between a Replica server and a Standard server.</p>
<p>A production Horizon Connection Server should have 10 GB of RAM and 4 vCPU.</p>
<ul>
<li>In Horizon 7.2 and newer, each Horizon Connection Server can handle 4,000 connections.</li>
<li>In Horizon 7.1 and newer, each Horizon Connection Server can handle 2,000 connections.</li>
</ul>
<p>To install Horizon Connection Server Replica:</p>
<ol>
