				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f4041626780d9da2748f3df4c8903716?s=56&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f4041626780d9da2748f3df4c8903716?s=112&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-56 photo' height='56' width='56'/>						<b class="fn">Sean</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

