						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25cdf50f43791cd43a58bd1f08f68f61?s=56&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25cdf50f43791cd43a58bd1f08f68f61?s=112&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-56 photo' height='56' width='56'/>						<b class="fn">Juan Lopez</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://www.carlstalhood.com/vmware-horizon-7-connection-server/comment-page-2/#comment-13730">
